  "What is the definition of 'air resistance' in the context of free fall?": "",
  "The force that air exerts on a moving object, opposing its motion through the air": "",
  "The force of gravity that pulls all objects toward the center of the Earth": "",
  "The friction between an object and the ground surface it slides across": "",
